column43: There is a break in deliveries between FY10 and FY11 procurements but the production line does not shut down.  The contractor slowed production deliveries due to a subcontractor facility chemical explosion in the 3rd quarter of FY12.  The Government is working to keep the production schedule healthy.  FY10 deliveries will be delayed due to reduced production to prevent a shut-down due to limited quantities of missile motors.
